{"tid":1918075,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[笑看風雲] 財政司司長辦公室 繼續密切留意市況發展","createTime":"2020-03-10T00:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T01:10:35.000Z","uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6d20b54f046c2fb205bbae7a128f0547099b1b","tid":1918075,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">繼續坐係辦公室嘅茂波兄咁講，我個心都當堂定一定</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長辦公室：面對市場波動會<span style=\"color: red;\">一如既往</span>嚴陣以待<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長辦公室晚上發新聞稿，指今日香港股市隨外圍因素相應下挫，市場表現與主要區內市場一致，雖然波幅及成交額較大，但股票、期貨及衍生工具市場如常<span style=\"color: red;\">有序運作</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港交所各項運作<span style=\"color: red;\">妥善進行</span>， 證監會亦一直密切監察場內場外的交易活動，外匯市場保持<span style=\"color: red;\">有序運作</span>，銀行體系亦<span style=\"color: red;\">運作正常</span>。<br />\n<br />\n財政司司長辦公室說，金管局會繼續維持香港的貨幣及外匯市場<span style=\"color: red;\">有序運作</span>，根據聯繫匯率制度，確保貨幣穩定；又指過去幾年做了多輪防震措施和壓力測試，加強市場抵禦衝擊的能力，提升對相關機構以至市場行為的監管，強調面對市場波動會一如既往，嚴陣以待，<span style=\"color: red;\">繼續密切留意市況發展</span>，適時加固防衛措施。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513422-20200309.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513422-20200309.htm&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSvsf6ZhrNwlVLGl95Ukzwcs%3D&h=48d660f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513422-20200309.htm&h=e0463e6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513422-20200309.htm</a>"},{"pid":"045ee8e18079f5928e5e1cbf978025aea4c0be21","tid":1918075,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T00:53:02.000Z","msg":"毒撚性格，得個望字"},{"pid":"713769d50cae826ed372f3acec8c9a9621a6af06","tid":1918075,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T00:53